ivardefs.name: applicability
ivardefs.desc: Whether the cost applies to in-network or out-of-network providers (in-network; out-of-network; other).

ivardefs.name: qualifiers_
ivardefs.desc: Additional information about the cost, such as information about funding sources (e.g. HSA, HRA, FSA, RRA).

ivardefs.name: type
ivardefs.desc: Type of cost (copay; individual cap; family cap; coinsurance; deductible).

ivardefs.name: value
ivardefs.desc: The actual cost value. (some of the costs may be represented as percentages rather than currency, e.g. 10% coinsurance).

properties.desc: List of the costs associated with a specific benefit.
